</div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="vertical" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2l8rr2:-trigger-ab3c9bd0-d77c-471d-9e6d-b7a9ae3288d51" id="radix-:R2l8rr2:-content-ab3c9bd0-d77c-471d-9e6d-b7a9ae3288d51" tabindex="0" style="display:none"><div data-rid="0ebd950f-331e-4b06-8bbf-0bd27fa4e21c" class="r-4e6i3u"><div data-rid="493ac7d2-daba-459a-853a-61bb5a26287d" class="r-14f1i27 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Simply&nbsp;add Hen Harmony to your flock’s drinking water based on the total amount of water in the waterer. Mix thoroughly before offering to hens.</p><p><br></p><h3>How Often Should I Use It?<br></h3><p><strong>1–8 chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every 3 months</strong><br><br></p><p><strong>9–14 chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every 2 months</strong><br></p><p><br><strong>15–21+ chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every month</strong></p></span></div></div></div><div data-state="active" data-orientation="vertical" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2l8rr2:-trigger-8d9953c1-cc12-4ae0-9174-996454dd11e82" id="radix-:R2l8rr2:-content-8d9953c1-cc12-4ae0-9174-996454dd11e82" tabindex="0" style="display:contents;animation-duration:0s"><div data-rid="46432e67-ca14-40b5-b390-5e531c1b1c7c" class="r-3q9djw"><div data-rid="fbb8cb01-680a-43bd-959b-30f66686c310" class="r-cf2j1c alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>💧 <strong>Supports hydration & electrolyte balance during stress</strong><br>Heat, cold, and stress can quickly disrupt fluid balance. This helps support hydration and electrolytes so hens can maintain normal function during demanding conditions.</p><p><br></p><p>🦠 <strong>Supports gut balance & beneficial bacteria</strong><br>Stress can upset digestive balance. This helps support a healthy gut environment so digestion stays steady when hens are under pressure.<br><br>🐔<strong>Helps hens cope with heat, cold & environmental stress</strong><br>Seasonal and environmental changes can strain a hen’s sy